Hi,

With Git: Rev {master} 81f120d the following input file:

    molecule chromium_dimer{
    0 1
    symmetry d2h
       Cr   0.0000   0.0000   0.0000
       Cr   0.0000   0.0000   1.6788
    }
    
    set {
      basis cc-pvdz
    
      guess sad
      scf_type pk
      reference rhf
      INTS_TOLERANCE 0.0
      D_CONVERGENCE 1e-12
      E_CONVERGENCE 1e-12
    }
    
    energy('scf')

hangs for more than 1 hour on

      SCF Guess: Superposition of Atomic Densities via on-the-fly atomic UHF.

pyscf and molpro take only seconds (the total number of orbitals is 86).

Best wishes,
Sebastian

